Balancing power in the "orient" is going to be a new game with N Korea and Iran each dveloping advanced nuclear tech.
<br />

<br />
Iran doing business with India could be a major stabilising thing.  These peoples doing business at a state level means less likely they will want to shoot at each other.  Iran, Pakistan and India relying on each to be friendly may be a good thing.<br />
