Various biological samples sold to the department of agriculture and the department of health. And then used for military purposes.
<br />

<br />
US helped with intel for gassing Iranian troops.
<br />

<br />
US sold helicopters to Iraq used to gas the Kurds. The US removed Iraq from its list of terrorist sponsors to do this. The helicopters were sold as farming equipment and confiscated by the Iraq government as soon as they arrived. It's likely the US knew this was the plan.
<br />

<br />
Cluster bombs. This was very illegal but done in a round about way. The USA sold a cluster bomb manufacturing plant and technology to Chile. This is illegal so it was sold as "scrap metal." Chile sold the cluster bombs to Iraq. These munitions were used in the Iran/Iraq war and on the Shi'ites during their uprising. Dunno if they were used on the Kurds. 
<br />

<br />
I believe the USA also did some political fanangiling so that weapons could be sold to countries in the area then quietly moved to Iraq. Not sure on specifics. Books have been returned to the library months ago.
<br />

